body:
I'm afraid there is still an issue with the implementation of this extension.
With just this simple test
```cpp
    Assimp::Importer importer;
    auto scene = importer.ReadFile("TextureTransformTest.glb", aiProcess_TransformUVCoords);
    Assimp::Exporter exporter;
    auto res = exporter.Export(scene, "glb2", "TextureTransformTest.glb", 0);
```
This is the output I get:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35391922/103138050-db37b300-46ce-11eb-8682-e41d2f40021b.png)

Plus it would also be a good thing to export the uv transform as an extension without modifying the UVs by applying the postprocessing `aiProcess_TransformUVCoords`.
